feature_bullets: [" Interesting and Fun: this magnetic drawing board is not just a box of toy, but also a toy for developing wisdom, which can exercise children's innovation ability, hands on ability, hand eye coordination, logical thinking and concentration, funny and meaningful"," Elastic Magnetic Pen: this nib of magnetic pen has a built in spring, which is retractable, making drawing more smooth; The tip of the pen is made of magnetic material, which is reliable to use; The magnetic pen is made of ABS material, so you don't have to worry about chewing"," Easy to Use: simply point the magnetic tip of the pen at each hole to move the magnetic beads to the surface and let your kids unleash their creativity; To reset, just use the side of the pen to push them down or smooth with your hand"," Multi Occasion Use: we can take this activity board to long car trips, restaurants waiting for dinner, and anywhere they need to be entertained, bringing a nice using experience"," Magnetic Touch Board: there are 3 boards in the package, which are red, blue and black; The size of the drawing board is 6.88 x 8.46 inch; The magnetic drawing board adopts a panel to avoid balls falling off and children eating by mistake, making it safer"]
